content: taofengno1: Merged a significant bugfix PR #2048 that updated regex to allow Unicode characters in message processing, involving extensive code changes across 1451 files (+81949/-43394 lines). Activity was sporadic, being active on only 2 days this month, with contributions primarily focused on bugfix work (67%) and feature development (33%).
